&gt;Here is an example recording from today. This is a prototype dual 
&gt;phototransistor optical mic. It&#39;s a very simple device. I turned up the 
&gt;levels on the radio and now I can hear some &#39;control tones&#39; between voices. 
&gt;I have heard these tones in the past very faint. The first voice is robotic 
&gt;the second normal
&gt;&quot;Good testing his circuit....That&#39;s awesome&quot;
&gt;
&gt;Dave
&gt;
