&gt;
&gt;Yes, the speaker is about a foot from the lamp/phototransistor combo. 
&gt;Volume has to be adjusted so the mic does not overload, it is a touchy 
&gt;adjustment of audio and flame level. If the flame is set too high the unit 
&gt;generates lots of noise from the flutter of the flame. Also the room should 
&gt;be dark and computer monitor turned down to reduce noise the mic will pick 
&gt;up produced stray light sources.
